item.title: Paying 100k cash for helping me work a auto alcher
item.dc:creator: @Enz0 Enz0
item.description:
@Enz0 wrote:

[code]program alcher;

{.include SRL/SRL.scar}

const

alchtimes=4000;//amount of trips you wish to do

var

tripsdone:Integer;

procedure setup;

begin
setupsrl;
end;

procedure findrandoms;
begin
if(findmod) then begin
logout;
end;
end;

procedure pradzia;
begin
mouse(712,323,0,0,true)
mouse(712,323,0,0,true)
end;

procedure highalch;
begin
DisguiseScar(‘Now High Alching’);
mouse(711,323,0,0,true)
wait(2000+random(700));
mouse(711,323,0,0,true)
tripsdone:=tripsdone+1;
DisguiseScar(‘Done High Alching’);
end;

begin
pradzia;
repeat
setup;
findrandoms;
highalch
MouseSpeed := 20
until
(tripsdone=alchtimes);
logout;
end.[/code]This isn’t mine, I just picked it up looking though the fourms, enjoy.
